[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Disable inflation]]
A [[en/Community/Patches/Patches]] that completely disables [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Inflation]]


== Description ==
All prices stay constant throughout the whole game with this patch. This way you can easily see how much more profit you are making compared to the recent years.


== Use ==
[[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Inflation]] is enabled by default. You can disable it through the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Configuring patches/Economy|configure patches -> economy]] window or use the following syntax in [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Openttd.cfg]]:
<pre>[patches]
inflation = false</pre>